text: Pilaki is a Turkish dish. Pilaki or Piłaki may also refer to *Piłaki, Mrągowo County, a settlement in Gmina Sorkwity, Poland *Piłaki Małe, a village in Gmina Budry, Poland *Piłaki Wielkie, a village in Gmina Pozezdrze, Poland *Żery-Pilaki, a village in Gmina Grodzisk, Poland *Olga-Afroditi Pilaki (born 1989), Greek rhythmic gymnast
title: Pilaki (disambiguation)
